<div class="section sign-up__form">
<div class="container">
  <div class="wrapper">
    {{!-- <div class="col col--8"> --}}
    <div class="signup__header">
      <!--h1 class="signup__title h1--light">Command line installation</h1-->
      <h2>Command line installation</h2>
      <p>Now you can install our command line tool <code>reco</code>. Choose your operating system and follow the instructions.</p>
    </div>
      <h3>Linux</h3>
      <p>Run the following from your terminal, you may be asked to enter your password. <code>reco</code> will then be available in new terminal sessions.</p>

      <pre>curl -LO https://s3.amazonaws.com/reconfigure.io/reco/releases/reco-v0.3.3-x86_64-linux.zip \<br>
&amp;&amp; unzip reco-v0.3.3-x86_64-linux.zip \<br>
&amp;&amp; sudo mv reco /usr/local/bin</pre>

      <h3>OSX</h3>
      <p>Run the following from your terminal, you may be asked to enter your password. <code>reco</code> will then be available in new terminal sessions.</p>

      <pre>curl -LO https://s3.amazonaws.com/reconfigure.io/reco/releases/reco-v0.3.3-x86_64-apple-darwin.zip \<br>
&amp;&amp; unzip reco-v0.3.3-x86_64-apple-darwin.zip \<br>
&amp;&amp; sudo mv reco /usr/local/bin</pre>

      <h3>Windows</h3>
      <p>If you're a Windows user you have two options for installing <code>reco</code>, either download our <a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/reconfigure.io/reco/releases/reco-v0.3.1.exe" target="_blank">installer</a> or, if you prefer, launch Powershell as administrator and paste the following commands. <code>reco</code> will then be available in new terminal/Powershell sessions.</p>

      <pre>Invoke-WebRequest https://s3.amazonaws.com/reconfigure.io/reco/releases/reco-v0.3.3-x86_64-pc-windows.zip -OutFile reco-v0.3.3-x86_64-pc-windows.zip;<br>
Expand-Archive -Path reco-v0.3.3-x86_64-pc-windows.zip -DestinationPath C:\reco -Force;<br>
setx PATH "$env:path;C:\reco" -m;</pre>

      {{link-to "Back" "sign-up.goal" class="btn"}}
      {{link-to "Check everything's working" "sign-up.getting-started" class="btn"}}
    {{!-- </div> --}}
  </div>
</div>
</div>
